{"tid":689396,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"庭上灑淚談肛交 歌手稱是第一次","createTime":"2018-06-04T04:55:51.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T16:06:55.000Z","uid":1426,"like":18,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"ac2d76151e46902619696f55cc72792a920837a2","tid":689396,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:55:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20130911/large/1378891763_7daa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20130911%2Flarge%2F1378891763_7daa.jpg&h=aba13b07&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n被告梁柏廷（右二）與盧海鵬合照。<br />\n<br />\n年青歌手梁柏廷（Jero）被控用肛交片段勒索男同志案，梁下午繼續出庭自辯，他否認勒索之餘反指實是遭事主雞姦，更在庭上流下男兒淚，指自己是第一次跟男人肛交，當日感到痛楚，他認為自己還年幼，「原本打算大個啲先諗性的事」，法庭更一度要休庭讓他平伏心情。<br />\n<br />\n現年21歲的梁柏廷，指當日遭事主雞姦後認為對方要負責任，於是向對方借錢，又指由於當時他剛簽下唱片公司並已拍好唱片封套，有自己的歌迷會及歌迷專業、曾與盧海鵬同台演出、獲楊受成胞弟聘請到其酒吧演出等，有感事業剛起步，以免被傳媒知道自己是同性戀者，所以未有報警。"},{"pid":"8264240d6f8f29f8c34f3b8bbe37634f6688e93e","tid":689396,"uid":1426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T04:57:13.000Z","msg":"TL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aac9f77153186c626c67539888a1ca5868047bc9","tid":689396,"uid":22839,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:00:04.000Z","msg":"指自己是<span style=\"color: red;\">當日第一次</span>跟男人肛交"},{"pid":"eb28075330c8e7707f751a32a3ba68a0db926672","tid":689396,"uid":3244,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:00:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6d84f2392951fca63b9913fd02fb9cc50b74adca","tid":689396,"uid":79562,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"party with TL<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72c8dcc7d64e4178d390fec37730fd882822e2c6","tid":689396,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-04T05:09:23.000Z","msg":"感動既係 波台清們終於留意到TL既才華<img src=\"/asse